IINCHIP_REG

Detailed Description

IINCHIP_REG defines register group of W5300. IINCHIP_REG includes 4 sub-group.

  • MODE_REG : Mode register
  • IDM_REG : Indirect mode register group
  • COMMON_REG : Common register group
  • SOCKET_REG : SOCKET register group

Note:
IDM_REG can be only used in indirect address mode.
